	<h2 >http to https</h2><div>
	<h4>Firefox</h4> “Options” → “Advanced” → “Certificates” → “View Certificates” → “Authorities”<br>
	<h4>Windows </h4>“Control Panel” → “Internet Options” → “Content” — “Certificates” → “Trusted Root Certification Authorities / Intermediate Certification Authorities”<br>
	<h4>Mac </h4>“Applications” → “Utilities” → “Keychain Access.” Under “Category,” pick Certificates”</div>

